'''Zcash'''是一種[[去中心化|去中心化]]、[[开源|开源]]的[[加密|加密]][[互联网|互联网]][[货币|货币]]。与[[比特币|比特币]]相比，其更注重于隐私<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://news.bitcoin.com/snowden-zcash-bitcoin-risks/ |title=Snowden: Anonymous 'Zcash' Could Solve Bitcoin Surveillance Risks |accessdate=2016-10-08 |author=Jon Southurst |date=2016-06-07 |publisher=Bitcoin.com |language=en |archive-date=2022-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220401202518/https://news.bitcoin.com/snowden-zcash-bitcoin-risks/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url= |title=斯诺登：匿名Zcash项目可解决比特币的监视风险 |accessdate=2016-10-08 |author=隔夜的粥 |date=2016-06-08 |publisher=巴比特}}</ref>，以及对交易透明的可控性<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://bitcoinmagazine.com/articles/zcash-creator-on-the-upcoming-zcash-launch-privacy-and-the-unfinished-internet-revolution-1472568389 |title=Zcash Creator on the Upcoming Zcash Launch, Privacy and the Unfinished Internet Revolution |accessdate=2016-10-08 |author=Giulio Prisco |date=2016-08-30 |publisher=Bitcoin Magazine |language=en |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108114832/https://bitcoinmagazine.com/articles/zcash-creator-on-the-upcoming-zcash-launch-privacy-and-the-unfinished-internet-revolution-1472568389 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.wired.com/2016/01/zcash-an-untraceable-bitcoin-alternative-launches-in-alpha/ |title=Zcash, an Untraceable Bitcoin Alternative, Launches in Alpha |accessdate=2016-10-08 |author=Andy Greenberg |date=2016-01-20 |publisher=WIRED |language=en |archive-date=2022-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119082047/https://www.wired.com/2016/01/zcash-an-untraceable-bitcoin-alternative-launches-in-alpha/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。具体体现为：公有[[区块链|区块链]]加密了交易记录中的发送人、接收人、交易量；用户可裁量选择是否向其他人提供查看[[密钥|密钥]]，仅拥有此密钥的人才能看到交易的内容<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://z.cash/about.html|title = Zcash - About|accessdate = 2016-10-08|language = en|quote = Zcash is a decentralized and open-source cryptocurrency that offers privacy and selective transparency of transactions. Zcash payments are published on a public blockchain, but the sender, recipient, and amount of a transaction remain private.|archive-date = 2018-09-29|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180929023403/https://z.cash/about.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

